HEADWORD: Benison
<hw>Ben"i*son</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>beneysun</ets>, <ets>benesoun</ets>, OF. <ets>bene⟦ium⟧<?/un</ets>,
